                <a href="#features" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-600 block px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-base font-medium">Features</a>
                <a href="#how-it-works" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-600 block px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-base font-medium">How It Works</a>
